{"tid":1494523,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"機管局連外判工都清算！部份職員已備辭職信「齊上齊落」 機場或癱瘓","createTime":"2019-08-21T16:21:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-22T16:08:06.000Z","uid":19287,"like":38,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"231817db3330c611958ae469947318603b7e8868","tid":1494523,"uid":19287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T16:21:19.000Z","msg":"據了解，清算名單除機管局直屬員工外，機場外判員工也在清算範圍。(資料圖片)<br />\n<br />\n機管局繼突向兩名處理機場運作的資深經理級員工「開刀」後，局方內部今日傳出更多清算消息。據了解機管局高層已加緊清算，近日除要求各部門「捉鬼」交名單，交出8.5當日缺勤名單，亦試圖收集曾有份表態支持及協助8.12及8.13機場集會示威者的員工資料。據了解，清算名單除機管局直屬員工外，機場外判員工也在清算範圍。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n據指，周一被炒的兩名經理級人員，傳因拒絕就範決定向管理層「死諫」，向上級提交的部門「清算名單」中，只交上自己的名字。惟機管局管方堅持繼續大清算，據了解，短期內會陸續有機管局及外判職員「收大信封」。目前已有一批員工準備好辭職信，一旦管理層鐵腕清算前線職員，會與同袍「齊上齊落」辭職，消息指，屆時機場極可能「攬炒」，因人手不足而運作癱瘓。"},{"pid":"ab4bd589483f724dc473f9afd43329c222c757dd","tid":1494523,"uid":65439,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T16:23:25.000Z","msg":"無限期罷工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8b061e7b7e5d04c8eb9b0c163455e3e6dd1e6ed","tid":1494523,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T16:25:20.000Z","msg":"支持齊上齊落<br />\n<br />\n攬炒<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><i